Supposedly my bus (well, my former bus; I've sold it since then) is in other
Grateful Dead documentary movie, called Tie Died.  It's a red and tan '77
Westy, with a big "steal-your-face" tire cover on the nose (with a VW logo
in the skull).   Probably parked next to a high-top Adventure Camper.

